[install]
* These can be configured via the 'https://splunk:8000/en-US/app/sentrywire/setup' page

* frontend is used to generate the URL to download a PCAP from Splunk
frontend = <URL to Splunk instance>

* Should the PCAPS be downloaded to the Splunk instance for the user to download directly from Splunk?
return_pcaps = <on | off>